###

- **Template Method**`EvoAgent` 
- ****

### 

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[CLI rdagent] --> B[Scenario]
    B --> C[EvoAgent]
    C --> D[EvolvingStrategy]
    D --> E[RAG]
    E --> F[KnowledgeBase]
    C --> G[Coder]
    G --> H[LLM]
    H --> I[( Docker)]
    I --> J[Feedback]
    J --> K[Experiment]
    K --> L[UI]
```

## 3. 

### 
- **CLI **`rdagent/app/cli.py`  
   `fin_quant`, `data_science`, `general_model` 
- ****`rdagent/core/evolving_agent.py`  
  

### 
- ****`rdagent/core/evolving_framework.py`  
   `EvolvableSubjects`, `EvolvingStrategy`, `RAGStrategy` 
- **CoSTEER **`rdagent/components/coder/CoSTEER/`  
  
- ****`rdagent/scenarios/`  
   KaggleQuant `Scenario` 

### 
-  `.env`  LLM `CHAT_MODEL`, `EMBEDDING_MODEL` 
-  LiteLLM  OpenAIAzureDeepSeek 
- `.env`, `rdagent/core/conf.py`, `pyproject.toml`

### 
- **LLM **`litellm`, `openai`, `tiktoken`
- ****`chromadb`, `faiss`
- ****`torch`, `transformers`
- ****`streamlit`UI`docker``typer`CLI

###

- **Qlib**
- **Docker**
- **Streamlit** Web UI 

### 

```mermaid
graph LR
    CLI[CLI] --> Scenario[Scenario]
    Scenario --> Agent[EvoAgent]
    Agent --> Strategy[EvolvingStrategy]
    Strategy --> RAG[RAGStrategy]
    RAG --> KB[KnowledgeBase]
    Agent --> Coder[Coder]
    Coder --> LLM[LLM Backend]
    LLM --> Docker[Docker]
    Docker --> Feedback[Evaluator]
    Feedback --> Logger[Log Storage]
    Logger --> UI[Streamlit UI]
```
